      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cinnamon</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong> and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3 min, then add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for a further 2 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/352-3-x200.jpg",
