    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once reduced, remove the pan from the heat and stir in your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> spiced lamb & sweet potato curry</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>brown rice </strong>with a fork and season with a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
