      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced</strong> <strong>lamb & sweet potato curry</strong> over the<strong> brown</strong> <strong>rice</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
